race.description: Coolum At The Beach Resort Hcp (Bm65)
race.comment: NINJITZOU (4) loves it here around this circuit with two wins and a second from four starts and gets a jockey upgrade in the form of Thompson in the saddle. Out to the mile for the first time, but that doesn't look an issue off of what we've seen recently. Wouldn't surprise to see him go to the next level now. FIFTH FORCE (5) saves his best form for this mile journey and strips fitter third-up from the break. Sure to play a pivotal role. MANHATTAN'S (9) is usually thereabouts and can trouble the judge with any luck in running. HUSSY EMPRESS (11) is racing in good order and has to be included on the back of some good runs recently.
